Name: Candied Caltrops
AttributesDescription: Increases DEF and Max HP of all Resonators in the team by 18% and 15% respectively, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: One of the famous signature dishes of the Panhua Restaurant. Its sweet and soft taste is very popular among the children of Jinzhou.
